fields.abstract: Senior Director of Programming David Spero interviews musician Randy Bachman for "An Evening with Randy Bachman" at the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame and Museum on February 1, 2001. Bachman discusses writing the song "Taking Care of Business," his autobiographical book also titled "Taking Care of Business," and recent miscellaneous solo and reunion projects. Bachman performs "Taking Care of Business" and "Ain't See Nothing Yet."
